flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic review of supplier-managed inventory performance and demand forecasts]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve SMI performance metrics]
  N1 --> N2[Agent: Agentic AI - Analyze SMI performance and generate recommendations]
  N2 --> N3[PB: Remote Functions - Share demand forecasts with suppliers]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: Cortex Monitoring - Monitor VMI program parameters]
  N4 --> N5{Agent: Agentic AI - Collaborate with suppliers on inventory reduction initiatives}
  N5 -->|Primary| P1[Action: Automate SMI performance reviews and recommend remediation actions, share demand forecasts with suppliers and secure production commitments, continuously monitor and adjust VMI program parameters, collaborate with suppliers to implement inventory reduction initiatives]
  P1 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved revenue protection through better availability, optimized working capital, and enhanced OTIF performance]
  N5 -->|Supplier performance below threshold| B1[Initiate remediation actions]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Improved supplier adherence to SMI program terms]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Insufficient inventory levels detected| B2[Adjust VMI parameters]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Optimized inventory levels and reduced stockouts]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Excess inventory identified| B3[Collaborate on reduction initiatives]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Reduced working capital and COGS]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]